Emepụtara Registry Africa na 2017 iji jikwaa ngalaba Africa kacha elu
A malitereafrica na African Union Commission na 2017. N'afọ 2012, ICANN malitere usoro ngwa maka ngalaba ọhụrụ dị elu. A bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ndebanye aha na 26 Machị 2014 na Singapore.
Akwụkwọ makaafrica kwadoro ma kwado ya site na African Union na mwepụta gọọmentị mere na isi ụlọ ọrụ Africa Union Commission na 3 Julaị 2017 n'oge 29th African Union (AU) Summit.
Nkwado mpaghara Africa nke Africa gụnyere African Union Commission (AUC), AfriNIC, AfTLD, ITU, UNECA na Nepad.
